\mathcal B(Y)=\sigma\bigl(i^{-1}(\mathcal O(X))\bigr)=i^{-1}\bigl(\sigma(\mathcal O(X))\bigr)=i^{-1}\bigl(\mathcal B(X)\bigr)=\{A\cap Y,\ A\in\mathcal B(X)\}
